  "body": "Currently the probeAddr listens on *:44135 and [it is not configurable](https://github.com/kubernetes/helm/blob/e8e6ac5d7783808cc0bd1adad053bec339849647/cmd/tiller/tiller.go#L62). Together with the host networking option for tiller, installation gives unexpected external visibility for this listening point for any potential user.\r\nThis might have a configuration option, similarly to the [grpcAddr](https://github.com/kubernetes/helm/blob/e8e6ac5d7783808cc0bd1adad053bec339849647/cmd/tiller/tiller.go#L70), or in this case, I would even expect that is can be disabled entirely if not needed.",
